Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從後面把答案卡傳上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定期考試結束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離東日本預賽還剩3天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我對英文的長文很有把握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道那題是陷阱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸…陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(750,100)\frz270\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\fad(600,600)}第二十一首
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(680,200)\fn@MHGHagoromoTHK-Medium\frz270\fad(600,600)}猶見白雙袖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(640,280)\fn@MHGHagoromoTHK-Medium\frz270\fad(600,600)}飄飄大雪揚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那題假裝問時間 其實是問時速 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已經開始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也難怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且千早在考試期間 完全沒有談過歌牌的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直在忍耐著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わびぬれば いまはたおなじ なにはなる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相處相思苦 風雨早滿城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}搶到了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是平常的綾瀨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要牌被搶走了 明明都會往上或往旁邊看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視線沒有離開牌面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿水一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿正流動著一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個印象… 放置於身體當中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢！ 居然不等我們就開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾瀨快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也跟我比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比 我比 我比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子君 也請跟我來比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 稍等 我休息一會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}這次輪到我做讀手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 喜歡歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把新再一次帶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從夏季全國大賽過後 她在練習時總是有種焦慮感…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為見到了新？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又在想這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一樣… 會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たちわかれ いなばのやまの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下因幡道 松濤聞滿山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ゆふされば かどたのいなば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暮色門前降 滿田何朦朧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あしのまろやに あきかぜぞふく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搖搖鳴稻葉 蘆舍臨秋風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ほととぎす なきつるかたを ながむれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曙色朦朧裡 數聲啼杜鵑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真島！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不著做到那種地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類用不著那麼完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我沒唸錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早你沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在剛才的比賽中 真島把牌背出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒看牌 隨意唸出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只在腦子裡唸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本書上說 這樣對背誦的練習很有效…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百首和歌 不分順序一首也沒有重複背出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那是優點也是缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的腦袋裡裝的全是文字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握被唸出來的牌是很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不多去感受在競技線中移動的牌是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用眼睛去看 想像畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得害羞 所以根本不練習空揮吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把牌跟你之間的距離感記在心中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌需要頭腦和身體雙方並行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭腦和身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是想著要快要快…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是手卻跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你一起變強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你一起參加東日本預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要全部記住會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎樣贏啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在比賽途中記住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初期配置我只記住一半左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 這樣我會害怕失誤 不敢搶牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾瀨同學～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到每科的老師那裡問過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這次沒有不及格的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師那麼大聲叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王賽的預賽要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 喜歡歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 看這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了配合今天的東日本預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我準備了新縫製的袴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高額頭同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高額頭同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 這次大賽是跟炎熱的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不穿袴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一般的大賽上都會開空調
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這裡既不開窗 別說空調了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連換氣風扇也不能開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以超熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那麼嚴格？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為「聲音」很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西田呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在樓下 跟翠北歌牌會的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大江同學和駒野也是屬翠北歌牌會的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們經常受到他們的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 有很多內情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早正在集中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不錯 就這樣到第一輪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這裡有輸給女王20張牌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 須籐前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都三年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用準備考試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一志願可是國公立大學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易得到了高中選手第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中選手權
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高中選手權得到第一或者第二就能被推薦去有名的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便 成為女王也可以得到推薦去好的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 千早的腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞入了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多餘的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙個性真差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若宮詩暢據說比現在的名人還要強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想像不到贏過她的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我贏過須籐前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那賭一賭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天先敗退的一方要剃光頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的光頭跟男生的光頭不可能一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙絕對不是會當做玩笑就放過你的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把女人的性命竟然一不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}開場儀式要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}各位選手請集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得情緒高漲保持到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做無用的逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}一不小心×N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日正是適宜歌牌的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與這邊同時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近江神宮正在舉行西日本預選
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本取得第一名的話 不就是世界第一了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾瀨同學成為女王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11月將在這個歌牌會館舉行東西代表決定戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}開始了 開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了對戰表後請馬上就坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的對手是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的頭髮由我保護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇上了棘手的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棘手的對手 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是什麼都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}梨理華小朋友 拍一張怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}狀態如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}真不愧是大牌選手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}夏季的千葉大賽也得到了第一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立川梨理華 仙台的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟女王一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學四年級就升上A級
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說這孩子就是若宮詩暢的接班人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天才梨理華
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華 緞帶整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與無名的你受到的期待方式是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是小學6年級的Speed Star
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說綾瀨姐姐的速度超級快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請在場外觀戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽在看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天才梨理華
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與無名的你受到的期待方式是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原田老師 比賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一輪不戰而勝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以保持體力太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣史先生也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早在和立川梨理華比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會輸給小學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師之前跟千早說過「停止快速取牌」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不還是很快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}千早的武器怎麼看都是是直覺敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}難得她正在進步著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}這樣做不會抹殺掉難得的長處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}特別對手又是立川梨理華
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かくとだに　えやはいぶきの　さしもぐさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊吹艾草茂 無語苦相思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}幹的好 梨理華
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}これやこの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠去與相送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みちのくの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紛紛心緒亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}せをはやみ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急流巖上碎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}好輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算整個身體飛出去也十分輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不擔心手誤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽覺也非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我很像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵有點大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}讓我看看你的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常被戲弄 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}耳朵豎起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽幫我把頭髮梳起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌老師說我的耳朵很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能夠聽清楚的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是歌牌還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會比千早更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早從競技線退後了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かけじやそでの ぬれもこそすれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來去難留住 唯沾衣袖濕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまはただ　おもひたえなむ　とばかりを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此勞空候 無須傳消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:12:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}跟讀手的呼吸對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ひとづてならで　いふよしもがな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言斷癡念 也勝苦相思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}不是快而是正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於做得到的人也許很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而對於我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさそふ あらしのにはの ゆきならで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿院非白雪 風雨催落花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}我在進步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}向著前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふりゆくものは　わがみなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過眼雲煙散 身老嘆韶華
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為跟我相像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很清楚梨理華的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あひみての　のちのこころに　くらぶれば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自赴佳期後 相思更轉愁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興能和大人們一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱讚「快」時很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}むかしはものを おもはざりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾言懷念苦 始信無來由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おほけなく うきよのたみに おほふかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦海茫無際 佛前表至誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}空牌 手誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}雖然看起來梨理華壓制了場面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒有拉開牌數的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的對手應對得很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪個歌牌會的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華瞄準的牌明顯是這張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這張送給她來進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她沒有瞄準的牌也不能被搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適時地取牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lucky 能對上只有速度快的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 不要再憑速度快來取牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於明白是什麼意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華的情況不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對手看起來也不是很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是天才嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早步調不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細一點就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真地比對手就會失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速取牌也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速取牌也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能相信老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わがたつそまに すみぞめのそで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不才居比睿 墨袖護蒼生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:16:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}しらつゆに かぜのふきしく あきののは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:16:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清秋原野上 白露滾涼風
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 「しら」都還沒唸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是非常快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了嗎 剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比天才梨理華還要快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}つくばねの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望築波嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}きみがため はるののにいでて わかなつむ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原上採春芽 只為獻君嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ありあけの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰看無情月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手誤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あかつきばかり うきものはなし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斷腸唯此時 拂曉與君別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちぎりおきし させもがつゆを いのちにて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縱有空言在 命託原上蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用那麼拚命的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あはれことしの あきもいぬめり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老來驚露冷 今歲逝秋風
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:17:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}むらさめの つゆもまだひぬ まきのはに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:17:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驟雨頻頻降 枝頭露未乾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是歌牌還是別的都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能喜歡上某件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能喜歡上自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連對手都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破第一輪了嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廣史
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望給千早許多的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是敏銳的直覺 還有局勢的讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸 準確率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌牌最重要的是才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是才能也有等級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這一樣是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她需要武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不被女王和現任名人這樣的天才擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早姐姐 把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是梨理華的幸運標記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來梨理華不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然被稱為是若宮詩暢再世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她卻沒有相當的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那個女王是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼比較也太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨理華剛開始也一定這麼被人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為綾瀨同學具有歌牌的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直將這當做是自己的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不輕易地去碰觸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須籐同學 真不甘心啊 我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}第一輪真是艱苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師你不是為了留念才來挑戰的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得我是A級有出場權 我的目標是成為名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}千早突破了第一輪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}新也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼「要加油」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吃的那麼急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也 這個也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都灑出來了 真是太不莊重了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 村尾哥輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 輸給了西城大一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按理說是不應該會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村尾兩年前還向名人挑戰過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他最近都沒有在練習
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 第一輪贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝賀你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能回來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然南雲會的人數不少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有潛力成為名人的卻不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後就是你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也只是挑戰者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是贏不了名人周防久志的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村尾哥 村尾哥 跟我比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新變厲害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得在被你超過之前當上名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}千早突破了第一輪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}我也一定要成為東日本的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs28}新你要成為西日本的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二輪快開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位選手請就位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:29.01,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:34.14,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}それぞれの道を  見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:39.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  また歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:45.19,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}ふたつの想いが  めぐり会う  その日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:54.45,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}迷いながらも 夢の色重ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:22:00.08,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君を想うからこそ 強くなれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:04.88,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}きっと 終わらせない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:09.97,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:15.06,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}輝く明日を  見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま  ほら 響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:28.28,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌  この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:29.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻你我兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:34.14,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著各自不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:39.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻我又放聲歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:45.19,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}直到兩人的思念相邂逅的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:54.45,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在迷惘之中 也不放棄追逐夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:22:00.08,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}正因為我思念你 才能變得堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:04.88,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}一定 不會就這樣結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:09.97,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻你我兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:15.06,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著光輝閃爍的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:20.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻  你聽  歌聲響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:28.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你曾經教會我唱的歌謠  迴響於這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8\fad(200,200)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}本字幕由 流雲字幕組 製作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8\fad(200,200)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}翻譯：柿子 清越 link.n 後期：梅子 嘉兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:29.63,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.01,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:38.18,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.06,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.77,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:52.15,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:59.99,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:05.33,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:11.13,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.01,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:20.51,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:29.63,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走過回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.01,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微風輕輕吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:38.18,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}閒話家常也異常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.06,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依舊一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.77,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我們常常相約等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:52.15,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然記得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:59.99,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在我心懷強烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:05.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}有什麼在目標之處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:11.13,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在的話似乎能抓住
